oding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-and-Kate-Cassidy-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故歌手<a href="/artists/Liam-Payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>的女友凯特·卡西迪在这位歌手不幸去世后向他致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独唱艺术家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>成员于周三（10 月 16 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡。阿根廷检察官办公室透露，这名31岁的男子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">的死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p>今天（10 月 18 日），卡西迪（Cassidy）自 2022 年以来一直与佩恩保持着恋爱关系，并在佩恩去世前几天与他一起旅行。今天（10 月 18 日），卡西迪在她的 Instagram 故事中向这位“Strip That Down”歌手致敬。</p><p> “谢谢你们给我的所有善意的话语和爱，”她的信息开头说道。 “我完全不知所措。过去几天的一切都感觉不到真实。我请求并祈祷你能给我恩典和空间来私下解决这个问题。” </p><figure id="attachment_3804245" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804245" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804245" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page.jpg" alt="凯特·卡西迪·利亚姆·佩恩致敬。图片来源：Kate Cassidy 官方 Instagram 页面的屏幕截图" width="1500" height="2369" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page-400x632.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page-800x1263.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page-696x1099.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page-1392x2198.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Kate-Cassidy-Liam-Payne-tribute.-Credit-Screengrab-from-Kate-Cassidys-official-Instagram-page-1068x1687.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804245" class="wp-caption-text">凯特·卡西迪·利亚姆·佩恩致敬。图片来源：Kate Cassidy 官方 Instagram 页面的屏幕截图</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_YExtHN1fB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-ra